      "content": "surrender sounds almost peaceful, honestly. if everything is just an inevitable void anyway, then fighting against it feels so stupid. it's like we're all just pretending we matter to make the fear go away. if the most logical end for everything is just... nothingness, then why is it considered so wrong to just want to reach that stillness sooner?",
